- Can I help you?

237
00:31:24,867 --> 00:31:28,529
Uh, yes, I am looking for someone
who would have known this woman.

238
00:31:30,005 --> 00:31:32,496
She studied here maybe
35 years ago.

239
00:31:34,542 --> 00:31:36,066
